==反響==
===專業評價===
本劇在評論界中受廣泛好評。《[[影音俱樂部|影音俱樂部]]》的Todd VanDerWerff正面評價本劇，認為它和其它那些有不少家長和成人作為死忠粉絲的節目不同，可以給人帶來「完全、毫無保留的樂趣」，且沒有[[犬儒主義#當代的犬儒主義|憤世嫉俗]]的元素。他稱讚了角色有風格的設計、劇情以兒童節目標準來看的複雜度和那些讓家長一樣也能樂在其中的有趣笑話，並給予本劇「B+」評分<ref name="AVClub">{{en}}{{cite web|url=http://www.avclub.com/articles/my-little-pony-friendship-is-magic,55168/|title=My Little Pony Friendship Is Magic|first=Todd|last=VanDerWerff|date=2011-04-29|work=[[The_A.V._Club|The A.V. Club]]|accessdate=2011-04-30|archive-date=2013-11-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131114235837/http://www.avclub.com/articles/my-little-pony-friendship-is-magic,55168/}}</ref>。本劇也因其幽默感和道德感被《[[今日美國|今日美國]]》的Brian Truitt所讚賞<ref>{{en}}{{cite web|last1=Truitt|first1=Brian|title='My Little Pony' plants a hoof in pop culture|url=http://www.usatoday.com/story/life/2012/11/26/my-little-pony/1725375/|website=usatoday.com|accessdate=2014-06-29|date=2012-11-26|archive-date=2022-06-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220606194926/https://www.usatoday.com/story/life/2012/11/26/my-little-pony/1725375/}}</ref>。《影音俱樂部》的Genevieve Koski後來評論說《友情就是魔法》是一個縱使被認為是「適合小女孩的」但卻依然能觸碰到書蟲文化、使作品獲得更大受眾面歡迎的一個典型範例<ref>{{en}}{{cite web|url = http://www.avclub.com/articles/why-should-grown-women-be-ashamed-of-holding-onto,58423/|title = Why should grown women be ashamed of holding onto their adolescent passions?|first = Genevieve|last = Koski|date = 2011-07-05|accessdate = 2011-07-05|work = The A.V. Club|archive-date = 2013-10-02|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20131002113603/http://www.avclub.com/articles/why-should-grown-women-be-ashamed-of-holding-onto,58423/}}</ref>。關注兒童節目育兒及教育方面的機構[[Common_Sense_Media|Common Sense Media]]的Emily Ashby給了本劇五星中的四星，強調本劇所帶出的有關友情、忍讓和尊重的信息，不過同時也建議家長小心「他們子女對與角色有關的書本、玩具等不同領域的產品線的渴望」<ref name="CommonSenseMedia">{{en}}{{cite web|url=http://www.commonsensemedia.org/tv-reviews/my-little-pony-friendship-magic|title=My Little Pony Friendship Is Magic – Television Review|publisher=[[Common_Sense_Media|Common Sense Media]]|first=Emily|last=Ashby|date=2011-01-30|accessdate=2011-05-09|archive-date=2012-04-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120405225530/http://www.commonsensemedia.org/tv-reviews/my-little-pony-friendship-magic|dead-url=no}}</ref>。《[[L.A._Weekly|L.A. Weekly]]》的Liz Ohanesian則提到本劇「有關友情的信息十分真摯、但同時也從不自視過高」<ref>{{en}}{{Cite news|url = http://blogs.laweekly.com/arts/2012/05/my_little_pony_brony_art.php|title = My Little Pony Project Brings Bronies and Pegasisters to Toy Art Gallery|first = Liz|last = Ohanesian|date = 2012-05-07|accessdate = 2012-05-07|work = [[L.A._Weekly|L.A. Weekly]]|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20120510045422/http://blogs.laweekly.com/arts/2012/05/my_little_pony_brony_art.php|archive-date = 2012-05-10|dead-url = yes}}</ref>。為《[[連線|連線]]》網站撰寫「[[GeekDad|GeekDad]]」專欄的Matt Morgan稱讚「孩之寶重啟這個存在已久的項目並加入少許極客元素」使得它能成為少數幾個「目標是小女孩、但卻同時也能讓一個極客爸爸和女兒一起樂在其中的節目」<ref name="geekdad">{{en}}{{cite journal|url = http://archive.wired.com/geekdad/2011/09/could-my-little-pony-be-raising-the-next-generation-of-geeks/|title = Could My Little Pony Be Raising the Next Generation of Geeks?|first = Matt|last = Morgan|date = 2011-09-17|accessdate = 2011-09-17|work = [[Wired|Wired]]|journal = |archive-date = 2021-05-12|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210512053118/https://www.wired.com/2011/09/could-my-little-pony-be-raising-the-next-generation-of-geeks/|dead-url = no}}</ref>。《[[洛杉磯時報|洛杉磯時報]]》評論家Robert Lloyd認為本劇比之前的彩虹小馬卡通「更聰明、更時髦、美學上更成熟」，並讚譽其因「又聰明又活潑又精心設計、但也從沒可愛到可怕」而能同時吸引子女和家長的能力<ref>{{en}}{{cite news|url = http://www.latimes.com/entertainment/tv/showtracker/la-et-st-tv-picks-my-little-pony-sondheim-improv-doc-martin-20131205,0,1696291.story|title = TV Picks: "My Little Pony," Sondheim, Improv comics, "Doc Martin"|work = [[Los_Angeles_Times|Los Angeles Times]]|date = 2013-12-05|accessdate = 2013-12-06|first = Robert|last = Lloyd|archive-date = 2014-01-05|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20140105235541/http://www.latimes.com/entertainment/tv/showtracker/la-et-st-tv-picks-my-little-pony-sondheim-improv-doc-martin-20131205,0,1696291.story}}</ref>。《[[電視指南_(美國雜誌)|電視指南]]》則在2013年9月將《友情就是魔法》列為有史以來頭六十位最佳動畫節目之一<ref>{{en}}{{cite journal|url = http://www.tvguide.com/News/Greatest-Cartoons-TV-Guide-Magazine-1071203.aspx|title = TV Guide Magazine's 60 Greatest Cartoons of All Time|first = Rich|last = Sands|date = 2013-09-24|accessdate = 2013-09-24|work = [[TV_Guide|TV Guide]]|journal = |archive-date = 2018-07-10|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20180710095501/https://www.tvguide.com/news/greatest-cartoons-tv-guide-magazine-1071203/|dead-url = no}}</ref>。

《[[Ms._(雜誌)|Ms.]]》的Kathleen Richter卻認為《友情就是魔法》並無改變舊世代動畫那針對女孩、被她認為是「性別歧視、種族歧視、[[異性戀霸權|異性戀霸權]]」的本質，例如她認為本劇是在透過雲寶推廣「所有[[女權主義|-{zh-cn:女权主义;zh-tw:女性主義;zh-hk:女權主義;zh-sg:女性主义}-者]]都是憤怒、有男孩子氣的女同性戀者」的成見，同時指出截至當時出現的所有深色調小馬都在被「白色的霸主小馬」所奴役<ref name="ms richter">{{en}}{{cite journal|url = http://msmagazine.com/blog/blog/2010/12/09/my-little-homophobic-racist-smarts-shaming-pony/|title = My Little Homophobic, Racist, Smart-Shaming Pony|first = Kathleen|last = Richter|date = 2010-12-09|accessdate = 2011-07-07|work = [[Ms._(magazine)|Ms.]]|journal = |archive-date = 2021-03-21|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210321234520/https://msmagazine.com/2010/12/09/my-little-homophobic-racist-smarts-shaming-pony/|dead-url = no}}</ref>。蘿倫·浮士德回應說雖然雲寶的確有男孩子氣，但「本劇絕無明示甚至是暗示她的性取向」且「將有男孩子氣等同於同性戀不論對那樣的異性戀或同性戀者都不公平」，並進一步說明「顏色一向以來都絕非用於定義小馬的種族」<ref name="ms faust"/>。《[[Cartoon_Brew|Cartoon Brew]]》的作者Amid Amidi則對本劇的理念更為批判，認為這代表了「創作者主導電視動畫時代的終結」。文章中她表示將如浮士德這樣的人才放到一個玩具主導的節目中顯示整體行業都開始轉而製作為盈利而生的動畫（如和玩具[[商業搭配|搭配]]），以解決觀眾群日趨碎片化的問題，並總體來說「是向這一變化的屈服，代表了整個電視動畫產業舉起白旗的那一刻」<ref name="cartoon brew"/>。

===收視率===
《友情就是魔法》在第一季首播時約有每月平均140萬人收看，但在第一季完結後已增加至每月400萬人的收視率<ref name="oregonian">{{en}}{{cite news|url = http://www.oregonlive.com/entertainment/index.ssf/2011/09/seriously_my_little_pony_grown.html|title = Meet "bronies" – grown men who are fans of My Little Pony|first = Kelly|last = House|work = [[The_Oregonian|The Oregonian]]|date = 2011-09-17|accessdate = 2011-09-17|archive-date = 2021-05-12|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210512053036/https://www.oregonlive.com/entertainment/2011/09/seriously_my_little_pony_grown.html|dead-url = no}}</ref>，成為當時孩之寶旗下收視率最高的動畫<ref name="geekdad"/>。《[[Advertising_Age|Advertising Age]]》也報道本劇觀眾量在第一至第二季間翻倍<ref name="ad age">{{en}}{{cite journal|url = http://adage.com/article/special-report-americas-hottest-brands/america-s-hottest-brands-pony-friendship-magic/231166/|title = "My Little Pony: The Friendship Is Magic" Gains Unexpected Audience – Adults|first = Judann|last = Pollack|date = 2011-11-28|accessdate = 2011-11-28|publisher = [[Ad_Age|Ad Age]]|journal = |archive-date = 2011-11-30|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20111130023209/http://adage.com/article/special-report-americas-hottest-brands/america-s-hottest-brands-pony-friendship-magic/231166/|dead-url = no}}</ref>。Hub Network則報告2012年2月11日第二季中以情人節為主題的劇集「[[Hearts_and_Hooves_Day|Hearts and Hooves Day]]」是截至當時本劇收看量最多的一集，也是Hub Network所播放的所有節目中收視率第二高的，觀眾量則是去年同期的逾150%<ref>{{Cite press release|url = http://tvbythenumbers.zap2it.com/2012/02/16/my-little-pony-friendship-is-magic-fan-favorite-mare-a-thon-boosts-the-hub/120230/|title = Stellar Performance of My Little Pony Friendship Is Magic Fan-Favorite Marathon Powers The Hub to Strong Audience Gains|publisher = [[Hub_Network|The Hub]]|date = 2012-02-14|accessdate = 2012-02-16|deadurl = yes|archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20120421102530/http://tvbythenumbers.zap2it.com/2012/02/16/my-little-pony-friendship-is-magic-fan-favorite-mare-a-thon-boosts-the-hub/120230/|archivedate = 2012-04-21}}</ref>。不過這一記錄被2012年4月分兩部分的大結局「A Canterlot Wedding」所打破，成為截至當時Hub Network所播放的收視率最高的節目<ref name="ratings">{{en}}{{cite press release|date = 2012-04-24|accessdate = 2012-04-24|publisher = [[Hasbro|Hasbro]]|title = Hub TV Network Scores Record High Audience With Outstanding Performance of Special Royal Wedding of the Year on "My Little Pony Friendship is Magic"|url = http://investor.hasbro.com/releasedetail.cfm?ReleaseID=666931|archive-date = 2012-05-04|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20120504133258/http://investor.hasbro.com/releasedetail.cfm?ReleaseID=666931|dead-url = yes}}</ref>。

===榮譽===
