===影迷===
{{main article|彩虹小馬：友情就是魔法影迷}}
儘管目標觀眾群原為小女孩及其家長<ref name="wsj"/><ref name="tvguide defense">{{en}}{{Cite journal|url = http://www.tvguide.com/News/Bronies-My-Little-Pony-Friendship-Magic-1068692.aspx|title = Give Bronies a Break!In Defense of Adult My Little Pony Fans|first = Sadie|last = Gennis|date = 2013-08-01|accessdate = 2013-08-01|work = [[TV_Guide|TV Guide]]|journal = |archive-date = 2014-12-29|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20141229100045/http://www.tvguide.com/News/Bronies-My-Little-Pony-Friendship-Magic-1068692.aspx}}</ref>，《彩虹小馬：友情就是魔法》開播後卻意外成為了一個文化和互聯網現象，吸引了大量13至35歲的男性影迷<ref name="wired brony"/>。網絡上的回應可被追溯至在貼圖討論版[[4chan|4chan]]上<ref name="wsj"/>為回應Amidi對本劇和現時動畫趨勢看法的卡通和動畫粉絲<ref name="cartoon brew"/><ref>{{en}}{{cite web|url=http://www.cartoonbrew.com/tv/weve-created-a-bronster.html |title=We've Created A Bronster! |first=Jerry |last=Beck |date=2011-09-24 |accessdate=2011-09-25 |publisher=[[Cartoon_Brew|Cartoon Brew]] |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110930022140/http://www.cartoonbrew.com/tv/weve-created-a-bronster.html |archivedate=2011-09-30 }}</ref>，而這些討論引起了網絡上各界人士的關注和興趣，形成了龐大的、以「Brony」（「bro」和「pony」的[[混成詞|混成詞]]，意为“小马的兄弟”）或中文世界的「小馬迷」自稱的影迷群體<ref name=bnet>{{en}}{{cite news|url = http://www.cbsnews.com/8301-505123_162-49640313/my-little-pony-the-hip-new-trend-among-the-geekerati/|title = My Little Pony: the Hip, New Trend Among the Geekerati|first = Constantine|last = von Hoffman|date = 2011-05-31|accessdate = 2011-05-31|publisher = [[BNET|BNET]]|archive-date = 2012-03-14|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20120314002516/http://www.cbsnews.com/8301-505123_162-49640313/my-little-pony-the-hip-new-trend-among-the-geekerati/|dead-url = no}}</ref><ref>{{en}}{{cite news|url = https://www.bostonglobe.com/ideas/2011/12/02/secret-language-bros/kd1q6tKQxO15hxMYWQSirO/story.html|title = The secret language of bros|first = Erin|last = McKean|date = 2011-12-02|accessdate = 2011-12-02|work = [[The_Boston_Globe|The Boston Globe]]|archive-date = 2014-03-16|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20140316220943/http://www.bostonglobe.com/ideas/2011/12/02/secret-language-bros/kd1q6tKQxO15hxMYWQSirO/story.html}}</ref>，並催生了不同形式的創作、影迷網站和會議<ref name="wired brony"/>。較早一批影迷對於孩之寶官方和本劇劇組成員來講都是出乎意料的<ref name="rollingstone ingram"/><ref name="wired brony"/><ref name="national post"/><ref name="csm"/>，而他們也感謝並接受了影迷群體，在劇中和玩具中加入了給影迷致敬的元素<ref name="awn"/>，且在早期曾沒對一些影迷中有想法的創作提出法律干涉，允許它們繼續發展<ref name="sopa"/>。

